WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:02.040
Now we're getting somewhere.

2
00:00:02.040 --> 00:00:05.000
It was her FriendlyBook account
 that posted on social media

3
00:00:05.040 --> 00:00:07.040
getting us into this mess
 in the first place.

4
00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:12.120
If we can prove that DCI Crooks has been hacked,
 then we'll be able to clear our name.

5
00:00:12.840 --> 00:00:16.080
If a password has been changed,
 we need to reset again.

6
00:00:16.880 --> 00:00:20.160
The easiest way is to answer
 the security questions on her account

7
00:00:20.880 --> 00:00:24.080
I found some information online
 from various stuff she's been posting

8
00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:25.920
or been tagged in.

9
00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:27.400
You're a detective!

10
00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:29.560
You should be able to piece together
the information you need.

